## Frequently Asked Questions About Web Hosting
**What type of hosting do I need?**
The right hosting depends on your website's traffic and resource needs. Shared hosting is suitable for new websites, while a VPS is better for growing businesses. Our team can help you select the correct plan for your specific requirements.

**How long does it take to migrate my website?**
A standard website migration is typically completed within 24 hours. Our migration experts handle the entire process, making sure there is minimal downtime. We schedule the final switch at a time that is convenient for you.

**Do you guarantee website uptime?**
Yes, we provide a 99.9% uptime guarantee. Our infrastructure is built with redundancy to maintain high availability. We constantly monitor our servers to address any potential issues before they affect your website's accessibility.

**What kind of support do you offer?**
We offer 24/7 expert technical support through live chat, phone, and tickets. Our in-house support team consists of experienced technicians who can assist with any hosting-related issue, at any time of day
